{"id":1246,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":207,"title":"Conversation 107","subtitle":"Christmas Party Details","level":"B1","parts":15,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-107.1246/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/0-conversation-107.mp3","transcript":"Hey, Bertha!\nWhat time is the staff Christmas party supposed to begin?\nIt is two days away, right?\nYeah! We have a private room reservation at Kimchi Korean Bar at 5 pm.\nI'm sorry, I know everyone wanted to go to The Big Fish Co. like we normally do,\nbut we waited too long to book.\nKimchi Korean Bar should be fun though,\nI went last week and they have karaoke which I think should be fun!\nOh, no problem.\nI've been there before.\nCan you make sure we aren't too close to the speakers?\nLast time I was there, it was so noisy.\nGood point!\nI didn't think of that.\nI will call tomorrow to confirm.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:01:25","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hey, Bertha!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/1.mp3","time_start":0.83,"time_end":1.94},{"position":2,"content":"What time is the staff Christmas party supposed to begin?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/2.mp3","time_start":1.94,"time_end":4.86},{"position":3,"content":"It is two days away, right?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/3.mp3","time_start":4.86,"time_end":6.64},{"position":4,"content":"Yeah! We have a private room reservation at Kimchi Korean Bar at 5 pm.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/4.mp3","time_start":6.77,"time_end":11.87},{"position":5,"content":"I'm sorry, I know everyone wanted to go to The Big Fish Co. like we normally do,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/5.mp3","time_start":12.05,"time_end":16.81},{"position":6,"content":"but we waited too long to book.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/6.mp3","time_start":16.81,"time_end":18.56},{"position":7,"content":"Kimchi Korean Bar should be fun though,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/7.mp3","time_start":18.85,"time_end":21.12},{"position":8,"content":"I went last week and they have karaoke which I think should be fun!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/8.mp3","time_start":21.12,"time_end":24.82},{"position":9,"content":"Oh, no problem.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/9.mp3","time_start":25.17,"time_end":26.38},{"position":10,"content":"I've been there before.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/10.mp3","time_start":26.38,"time_end":27.68},{"position":11,"content":"Can you make sure we aren't too close to the speakers?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/11.mp3","time_start":27.68,"time_end":30.72},{"position":12,"content":"Last time I was there, it was so noisy.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/12.mp3","time_start":30.72,"time_end":33.29},{"position":13,"content":"Good point!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/13.mp3","time_start":33.58,"time_end":34.46},{"position":14,"content":"I didn't think of that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/14.mp3","time_start":34.46,"time_end":35.61},{"position":15,"content":"I will call tomorrow to confirm.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-107-2023-10-03-11-37-17/15.mp3","time_start":35.61,"time_end":37.49}]}